---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import ByteCapsule from "../assets/bytecapsuleit.jpeg";
import WIYP from "../assets/wellington.png";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<section
  class="my-10 w-full border-l border-gray-300 p-3 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start"
>
  <h1 class="text-red-400 text-xl font-semibold mr-10">Experience</h1>
  <div class="flex flex-col space-y-10">
    <!-- Experience 1 -->
    <div class="">
      <div class="flex justify-between w-full">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:border-l md:border-gray-300">
          <div class="mx-5">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-1">
              <Image
                src={WIYP}
                alt="Wellington Logo"
                class="h-6 w-6 mr-2"
                fit="cover"
                format="avif"
              />
              <h1 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center">
                Wellington In Your Pocket
                <span>
                  <a href="https://wellingtoninyourpocket.co.nz/home2/" target="_blank">
                    <Icon
                      name="gridicons:external"
                      class="ml-2 text-red-400"
                      width="18"
                    />
                  </a>
                </span>
              </h1>
            </div>
            <h3>Cloud Engineer</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Jan, 2023 - Present</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ml-5 mt-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          As a Cloud Engineer at "Wellington In Your Pocket", My role involves
          designing, implementing, and maintaining the backend architecture
          using various AWS services. I am responsible for ensuring scalability,
          reliability, and security of the cloud infrastructure to support the
          application's requirements. I work closely with cross-functional teams
          to understand project requirements and translate them into scalable
          and robust cloud solutions that drive the application's success.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience 2 -->
    <div class="">
      <div class="flex justify-between w-full">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="mx-5">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-1">
              <Image
                src={ByteCapsule}
                alt="Bytecapsule Logo"
                class="h-6 w-6 mr-2"
                aspectRatio={1 / 1}
                fit="cover"
                format="avif"
              />
              <h1 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center">
                Byte Capsule Ltd.
                <span>
                  <a href="https://www.bytecapsuleit.com/" target="_blank">
                    <Icon
                      name="gridicons:external"
                      class="ml-2 text-red-400"
                      width="18"
                    />
                  </a>
                </span>
              </h1>
            </div>
            <h3>Full Stack Developer</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">May, 2020 - Nov, 2022</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ml-5 mt-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          As a Full Stack Developer at Byte Capsule Ltd, I optimized application
          performance, developed and maintained a complex web application using
          the MERN stack, and implemented new features on the front-end using
          React. I collaborated with the product team to gather requirements and
          helped to attract new customers with improved application speed and
          reliability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
